Text.string: Vault Hunter! Good to see you!
Hey, Vault Hunter. Keep fighting the good fight!
I see ya.
Vault Hunter, you're alive!
Yo!
It's a good day to kill some COV!
How's that Pandoran sun treating ya?
How's that Pandoran moon treating ya?
It's a fine night to slaughter some bandits!
I'm gonna be a Crimson Raider some day. Put in a good word for me?
I gotta train harder if I'm gonna be good enough to join the Raiders.
Tyreen seems like a real bitch. Why do those bandit idiots hang on her every word like that? Oh yeah, because she claims that she's doing all this for them. Yeah, right.
Civilization is a little overrated, don't you think?
Always wanted to travel and see other worlds. Never thought I'd get the chance.
You ever been to Athenas? I heard their trees have flowers and everything!
I'm not feeling too well. You think I got the gut-rot?
I'm actually a pretty decent shot, y'know?
I need some new gear. Gotta get some cash first though. Which means it's time for some looting!
The Calypsos are monsters, but they ARE sort of entertaining...
As a native Pandoran, I gotta say, I didn't think bandits could get any stupider. But then they start worshipping those stupid Calypsos, who are totally stupid.
Pandora may be the junkyard of the Borderlands, but it'll always be home.
I wish we could wipe out all the bandits, and make Pandora a decent place for once. But I just don't see it happening.
Folks barely scrape by on Pandora, but most of 'em can't afford to leave. That's the truth of it.
I spent a lot of years hoping to strike it rich with some Eridian artifacts or something, but I never found anything. Guess I'm no Typhon DeLeon. Ngh.
Waited my whole life to leave Pandora. But it's actually pretty boring on this ship.
Never really thought I'd miss Pandora, but here I am missin' it.
Being on this ship means I'm one step closer to being a full on Crimson Raider. Pretty sweet.
Never got to live in the first Sanctuary, so being here with y'all is pretty righteous.
Y'all got showers somewhere on this ship?
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawn] Oh, wow...
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
Later, Vault Hunter!
If you want me to come with you, just say the word!
If you die, can I have your gear?
Good luck out there!
Crimson Raiders, what-what!
Do it for Roland!
Get out there and murder some COV!
Never die! That's an order!
Let's kill some bandits together sometime!
Bring me back a COV skull!
I need to freshen up my look. Junkyard-chic is getting old.
Oh crap. I just realized I'm gonna die someday.
Ugh. I need a shower.
I'd feel better about myself if I had more followers.
Time sure flies when you're sitting around on a spaceship not doing anything.
[rakk screech] And come on, rakk pet!||—Damn.
Vault Hunter isn't a title, it's a state of mind.
Moxxi is so glamorous. I wish I could be more like her.
What time is it? Can I start drinking yet?
Is it weird that I'm always talking to myself?
Can't remember the last time I had a piece of fruit.
I should get a new Bunkers and Badasses game going. It's been too long!
WHERE IS MY SANDWICH?!
I should get into ECHOcasting.
Ugh, I'm never gonna be rich.
Yeah!
All right!
Cool!
Yeah!
Yes!
Awesome!
I dig what you do!
Things are looking up!
All right! Good job!
[burps]
[burps]
[burps]
Could use some attention!
I'm still around, y'know!
It's me! Still me.
Raise your hand if you're bored.
Gotta keep the old arms limber!
Workin' on the old wave!
